    "However, gaps remain in unpacking the specific mechanisms through which green finance leads to environmental improvements, especially across development contexts (SDG 13).",
    "Another study by Bayram et al. (2022) examines how fintech solutions can promote sustainable finance in emerging market economies, using Turkey as a case study.",
